      "name": "Layer 19: \"Preventing the Invasion! The Pitch-Black Super Quantum!!\"",
      "effect": "Activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each effect of \"Layer 19: \"Preventing the Invasion! The Pitch-Black Super Quantum!!\"\" once per turn);\n\u25cf Target 1 Attack Position monster on the field; change it to Defense Position.\n\u25cf If you control a \"Super Quant\" monster: Special Summon 1 \"Super Quant\" monster from your Deck in Defense Position, with a different original Attribute from the monsters you control.\n\u25cf Set 1 \"Super Quant\" Trap from your Deck. It can be activated this turn.",
